                    {
                      "type": "span",
                      "value": "The paper \"OpenBA: An Open-sourced 15B Bilingual Asymmetric seq2seq Model Pre-trained from Scratch\" introduces a bilingual large language model tailored for Chinese-oriented applications."
                    }
